#javascript 

## before

```javascript
const foo = { bar: 42 }

Object.entries(foo).map((entry) => {
  //                     ^^^^^
  const [key, value] = entry
  console.log(key, value)
})
```

## after

```javascript
const foo = { bar: 42 }

Object.entries(foo).map(([key, value]) => {
  //                     ^^^^^^^^^^^^
  console.log(key, value)
})
```
